high_descs: Step forward, turn right, step forward, then turn left to come to the corner of the vanity.
Pick up the purple sprayer to the right.
Turn left, step forward, turn left, step forward, then turn right and step forward to the bathroom vanity.
Open the bottom right cabinet door, place the sprayer inside, close the door.
Turn  around, step forward, then turn left to face the trash can.
Pick up the sprayer out of the trash can.
Return to the bathroom vanity.
Open the bottom right cabinet door, place the sprayer to the right side, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Pick up two sprayers, place in bathroom cabinet.
